latestPosts.caption:
the ultimate skin hydration duo 🤍

skin elixir recipe: 
30g of peach gum 
10g of snow birds nest “gum tragacanth” 
5-10 large jujubes (remove pit) 
80g of rock sugar 
500g of water 
* cook for 30 mins and then add a handful of organic goji berries 

enjoy it hot or cold
